                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "岩雨"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素傷害</span>，召喚<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">岩脊</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/7998136/bd88dd4e84f0956abd3d34b19442d2c6_3898561732700111363.png",
                "id": "talent48686",
                "key": "地心",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "地心"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成3點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素傷害</span>，召喚<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">岩脊</span>，生成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">玉璋護盾</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">玉璋護盾</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">出戰狀態</span></p><p>為我方出戰角色提供<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">2點護盾</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/7998136/857631feb4f9832ee5644c9f6faf3a44_2246152286278601361.png",
                "id": "talent21129",
                "key": "地心·磐礴",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 5,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "地心·磐礴"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成4點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素傷害</span>，目標角色附屬<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">石化</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">石化</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">角色無法使用技能。</span>（持續到回合結束）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/7998136/c701cbbd15b971aaee458b19e71b4ced_1950952071881941288.png",
                "id": "talent27258",
                "key": "天星",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "天星"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">結束階段：</span>造成1點<span style=\"color: #FFE699\">岩元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/26/7998136/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_6713884535355909953.png",
                "key": "岩脊",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/26/7998136/905fb3dd007f1806491f7e9df8812d45_8486092581823844529.png",
                "title": "岩脊"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>和已附著的元素發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">結晶（冰）</span>：本傷害+1，我方出戰角色獲得1點護盾（可疊加，最多2點）。</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">結晶（水）</span>：本傷害+1，我方出戰角色獲得1點護盾（可疊加，最多2點）。</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">結晶（火）</span>：本傷害+1，我方出戰角色獲得1點護盾（可疊加，最多2點）。</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">結晶（雷）</span>：本傷害+1，我方出戰角色獲得1點護盾（可疊加，最多2點）。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/26/7998136/fd37cbfdd3b1b2c16e6e83fb0aa96889_3102688065165481571.png",
                "key": "岩元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "岩元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span></strong></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗1次<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">護盾</span></strong></p><p>此護盾所保護的角色受到傷害時，將會消耗護盾來抵消傷害。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/26/7998136/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_6314234393851109274.png",
